Original:
#c2#The bell atop the tower rang
for the fifth and final time,
cutting the stillness of the air.

All of these gravesites are empty;
they're essentially just memorials.
Except for Marle's, anyway...

...Adol, we'll be rooting
for you. Knock 'em dead,
man! ...Literally, if you can!

I'm also not someone you'd want to ask
for love advice. Aside from that,
though, I'm your man!

A pity gift won't make up
for your heinous actions,
young man. Repent! REPENT!

A present? I suppose this is to make up
for the fireball? Have you realized,
then, that I'm not your enemy?

Quickly, the final battle
awaits. I'll be fine;
you go on ahead.
